---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Our Story — YKS"
  description="The story behind YKS — beautifully made, practical printables for habits, focus and productivity. Built for people who want real tools without the fluff."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-20 prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="tracking-tight">We build the manuals we wish existed.</h1>

    <p class="lead">YKS was born out of frustration with overpriced, vague productivity content. We make beautiful, practical printables — guides, calendars and trackers — that actually help you get organized and ship. We keep the core library free on purpose, and fund the work with a small set of curated premium packs.</p>

    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>Every guide must be:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Battle-tested</strong> by real operators (not armchair experts)</li>
      <li><strong>Scannable and actionable</strong> — you should be able to implement something meaningful in under an hour</li>
      <li><strong>Honest</strong> about scope, time, and tradeoffs</li>
      <li><strong>Beautifully designed</strong> so the delivery matches the promise</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who makes this</h2>
    <p>We're a small team of designers, productivity nerds, educators and makers who build the tools we use ourselves — from habit trackers that actually stick to puzzles that sharpen focus. Every printable is tested in real life before it goes out, and designed to be immediately useful on paper.</p>

    <p class="text-sm text-text-subtle">We are not gurus. We make tools that work on paper.</p>

    <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-8 border border-border rounded-2xl bg-surface">
      <p class="font-medium">Interested in contributing or licensing a system?</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary mt-4 inline-block">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
